    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1888-01-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1888-01-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="31" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d31">
                <head>No. 31.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Tree</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-01-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 26,
                            1888</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 96.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Your dispatch (No. 289) of the 6th instant,
                        reporting your action under my instruction (No. 90) of the 7th ultimo
                        relative to the alleged <pb facs="0169" n="35" xml:id="pg_35"/> wrongs
                        inflicted on the American Baptist Missionary Union by Mr. Henry M. Stanley
                        and the Congo State authorities, has been received.</p>
                <p>Your report of the restitution of the steamer and indemnification of the
                        owners has been read with satisfaction.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">T. F.
                            Bayard.</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
